quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  5,32,"Ko sabu …óum min parliri e …ďi…ó…ďe Israa'iila …ďen, wonnde : "Kala bar…óo woŇčkii awaa wanaa joftanagol- gol woŇčkii maa bonni ka leydi, tawat o wa…óii wa bar…óo yim…ďe …ďeen fof, mo wuurnii ki kadi, o wa'ii wa on guurnu…óo yim…ďe …ďen fof". GooŇč…óii Nulaa…ďe amen …ďe gaddanii …ďe …ďanngannduyeeji, refti pellet, ko …ďuri …óuu…óude e ma…ď…ďe …ďaawo …óum, ko …ďe fantim…ďe( …ďurtinoo…ďe)ka leydi."
  5,33,"Ngandee njo…ďdi …ďeen ha…ďoo…ďe Alla e Nulaa…óo Makko on, hi…ďe yaha bonna ka leydi, ko nde …ďe mbaretee, maa …ďe dummbee, maa juu…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen e koy…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen ta∆īee luutindiree, maa …ďe ndiiwee e leydi ndin. ∆äuum …óon, no woodani …ďe koyeera ka aduna ; no woodani …ďe kadi ka laakara, lepte maw…óe."
  5,34,"Si wanaa …ďen tuubu…ďe ko adii on he…ďude feere ma…ď…ďe. Anndee pellet, Alla ko kaforoowo, jurmotoo…óo."
  5,35,"Eeheymon yo gooŇč…óim…ďe, kulee Alla, …óa…ď…ďiron e Makko jokkorgal, tii…óno…óon e Laawol Makko, mbelajo'o, on maloyte."
  5,36,"Pellet, …ďeen yeddu…ďe, sinno no woodannoo …ďe denndaagal ko woni ka leydi e yeru mun wonndude e …óum, fii yo …ďe coottor …óum immorde e lepte √Ďande Darngal, …ďe ja…ďantaake. No woodani …ďe lepte mu'us…óe."